high_descs: Turn to the right, go forward past the counter, hang a right, go forward, hang a left and go to the sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is in the sink.
Turn around, go forward, turn to the right, go forward to the fridge.
Open the fridge, use the knife to cut the potato just to the right of the lettuce into slices.
Put the knife down in the fridge right in front of the potato that was cut.
Pick up a slice of the potato and close the fridge.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right, go forward then go to the left to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink between the cup and spatula, turn the water on and rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn around, go forward, then hang a right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the clean potato on the shelf directly above the yellow handled knife, close the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put clean potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the sink.
Take out the yellow knife from the sink.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Slice the potato to the right of the lettuce in the fridge.
Place the knife in front of the lettuce.
Pick up a slice of potato from the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the sink to your left.
Wash the slice of potato and take it out of the sink.
Turn left and walk back to the fridge.
Place the slice of potato in front of the bowl in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed slice of potato along with a yellow knife in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and take three steps, then turn right and take one step, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle from the sink.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk across the room to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and cut the potato on the right side.
Place the knife in the fridge in front of the cut potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Place the potato in the sink to the left of the spatula, then turn the water on for two seconds, then pick up the slice of potato.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the slice of potato in the fridge, on the top shelf next to the bowl.
anns.task_desc: To cut and clean the potato.
